  <h2 class="tinylabel"><b>03</b> The Details</h2>

  <h3>The Problem</h3>

  <p>PowerFleet had the opportunity to showcase some of our new technology involving chassis and load sensing at the Freghtwaves F3 Virtual Conference in the Fall of 2021. The existing application that supported this technology was from acquisition and did not look like the current brand. </p>

  <h3>Building a New Reality</h3>

  <p>Taking existing data and functionality from the older application, I created a clickable prototype with Sketch and InVision that allowed us to simulate a few common workflows. I leveraged the vision board styling I had worked up previously, incorporating the new brand and a new look and feel on our core platform.</p>

