  <h3>Selling The Vision</h3>

  <p>I worked closely with Julia Grove, the head of marketing, and other SMEs in PowerFleet to create a script explaining these features' value through a six-minute video. Due to COVID, I filmed this in my home office and was the on-camera talent. I edited the presentation together and performed the audio post on it to get it ready to go out for the conference.</p>

